	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Clean it every once in awhile...you can even rebend the pins. No way to fix it other then getting a toploader nes. It's really not THAT hard to clean it every once in awhile. (make sure your games are clean before putting 'm in and dont blow on them)

		

		</td>
	</tr>
